Dialogue: 0,0:00:-01.-01,0:00:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.62,0:00:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.49,0:00:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.33,0:00:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.43,0:00:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.05,0:00:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.56,0:00:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.56,0:00:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.06,0:00:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.37,0:00:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.31,0:01:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.22,0:01:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.47,0:01:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.71,0:01:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.31,0:01:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.05,0:01:38.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Yuba"              "Nanohana"   "Katorea"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years have passed since\Na single drop of rain fell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the kingdom of oases.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing hope beyond turmoil,\Nthe people took up weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The burning land is now\Nenveloped by a sad bellowing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.83,0:01:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a mighty swell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.31,0:01:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After arriving in Alabasta,\NLuffy and the others
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.87,0:02:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,encountered Navy Captain Smoker.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.55,0:02:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There to save Luffy\Nin the nick of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was the man who controls fire:\NFire Fist Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.09,0:02:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace turned out to be\NLuffy's older brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.56,0:02:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ace and Luffy!\NHot Emotions and Brotherly Bonds"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.61,0:02:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that's a no-can-do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.42,0:02:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think you're Straw Hat's brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,White...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spark!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is a house on fire?!\N--No, it's no ordinary fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.13,0:03:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a fight between flame and smoke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.60,0:03:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did say he ate\Nthe Flame-Flame Fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Luffy! Is it true\Nthat guy's your brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.54,0:03:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! His name's Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You having a brother\Nisn't that surprising,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.08,0:03:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but what's he doing\Nin the Grand Line?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace is a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He left the island three years\Nbefore me to find the One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.56,0:03:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyways, let's hurry back to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's escape before\Nanyone comes after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.06,0:04:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I never thought I'd\Nsee Ace in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The path splits into two!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, left! Hear me, guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Nami-san! I'll follow\Nyou wherever you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough, pervy cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.22,0:04:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool! The fireball's gone even higher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems there really is no end to\Na fight between flame and smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it was already obvious enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.00,0:04:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Straw Hat's crew go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.13,0:04:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So is Ace! We've lost sight of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught Straw Hat for the\Nfirst time in the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.61,0:04:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Portgas D. Ace.\NYou simply had to get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and load the stuff!\NWe're leaving right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Set the sails!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:05:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Say. Are we leaving again just\Nafter we finally reached the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.79,0:05:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We only stopped by this town\Nto get what we're going to need.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.46,0:05:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're going to head up the\Nriver into the interior of Alabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.23,0:05:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our next destination is Erumalu,\Nthe City of Green.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Erumalu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick up the pace!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All set!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y'know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get the feeling we're\Nmissing someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.02,0:05:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So do I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We're missing\Napproximately one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.14,0:05:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.21,0:05:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the only one here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:06:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh! I guess my letting you\Nescape was pretty much pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.55,0:06:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.49,0:06:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.49,0:06:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't seen you in a while, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.52,0:06:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many years has it been?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.53,0:06:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Luffy. It looks like you\Nstill go at your own pace,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.20,0:06:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just like you did\Nsince you were a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.37,0:06:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, Ace! I was surprised\Nyou ate a Devil Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.14,0:06:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but besides that, you're the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like when you'd sneak into the fields,\Neat 100 watermelons,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then spit the seeds\Nout like a gun and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't me! That was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then you got big bumps right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was you, too!\NI watched and laughed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we're both the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.60,0:06:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This brings back memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, weren't your friends\Nlooking for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Ace. What are you\Ndoing in this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.88,0:07:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You mean you didn't get\Nthe message I sent to Drum?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drum?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's no big deal\Nor anything, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just in these waters\Non minor business,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.23,0:07:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I might look you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.90,0:07:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minor business?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.10,0:07:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a member of the\NWhitebeard Pirates now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the mark of the\NWhitebeard Pirates. It's my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy. Won't you join\Nthe Whitebeard Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends can come too, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured not. Just thought I'd ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard is the greatest pirate I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna help him to be\NKing of the Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And not you, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.87,0:08:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine!\NThen we'll just have to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't drink it all, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something must've happened in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.89,0:08:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smoker and all the\Nmarines left the ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is perfect! I'll use this\Nchance to escape somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be members of Baroque\NWorks if you know my codename!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Millions?! Hurry and untie me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we are members of Baroque Works.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.21,0:08:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we're Billions. Meaning we're\Ncandidates to be Number Agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 11. You're barely an agent.\NYou're not much stronger than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh! I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.03,0:09:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that, Billions.\NBut could you hurry and untie me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you gone, one of us can\Nbe promoted to a Number Agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's empty one of the Agents' seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.81,0:09:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist Ace is in this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Fire Fist Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Second Division Commander\Nof the Whitebeard Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can take down Ace,\Nwe're guaranteed to be Number Agents!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.47,0:09:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyways, let's look for your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting spotted by the\NNavy's always a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.21,0:09:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They might've gone back to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which harbor is your ship in?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:10:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I can't remember at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate ship captains usually\Nremember where they leave their ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are the same as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what kind of crew do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.01,0:10:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A swordsman who wants to be the\Nworld's greatest sword master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always wearing a haramaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A navigator who likes maps\Nand tangerines and money!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's a cook who\Nmakes really yummy food...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.86,0:10:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and there's a liar, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.09,0:10:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then a reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite the variety you got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We also have a princess and a duck now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.43,0:10:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all so interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.80,0:10:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say you're probably the\Nmost interesting of all, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.97,0:10:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, only a handful of people for a\Npirate crew... That's just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also want a musician!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:11:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there, Fire Fist Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,\Nthere's no place to run now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist Ace! Your head is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.43,0:11:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is it really okay to\Nset sail without Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy will be all over the harbors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.42,0:11:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to hide the ship first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.66,0:11:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be a cove ahead\Nthat's hidden from view!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll wait for things to\Ncool down, then look for Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeesh! He's always, always\Ncausing trouble like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:12:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a real reliable captain...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist Ace! Your bad luck ends here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Isn't that Straw Hat Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.29,0:12:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Now that you mention it--!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's worth 30 million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about lucky! Fire Fist Ace\Nand Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I have your heads, our promotion\Nis a hop, skip, and jump away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's find your ship.\NLet's go to the shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.22,0:12:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the--?! What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:13:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold the bastard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the--?! His arms stretched!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.97,0:13:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has Devil Fruit powers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare me like that, you jerks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.36,0:13:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't let 'em scare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rank of Number Agent\Nis riding on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! The ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See your ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys just never learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.17,0:14:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.21,0:14:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Over here! Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy. Go on--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.61,0:14:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! There he is! It's Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I found Luffy!\N--You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. That stupid face is definitely his.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.56,0:14:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-san! Tony-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.54,0:14:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 'bout that, Sanji, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you not know how to learn your\Nlesson?! I oughta gut you whole!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Do you have any idea how\Nmuch trouble you've caused?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to act somewhat like a captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:14:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.79,0:15:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right! Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ace?\N--Your brother was with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it okay to just leave him there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.16,0:15:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he'll be okay! Ace is strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.23,0:15:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.27,0:15:16.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He hadn't eaten the\NFlame-Flame Fruit a long time ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I still never beat\Nhim in a single fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's real strong, Ace is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.98,0:15:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a flesh-and-blood\Nperson you could never beat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the big brother of a\Nmonster is an even bigger monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I lost all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.62,0:15:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd win now if we tried!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume that's another groundless claim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.90,0:15:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can win what now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Ace! This is the crew\NI was talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Thank you all for taking\Ncare of my little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Oh, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:16:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be a bit much for\Nyou to handle too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of 'im.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably have lots\Nof catching up to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come in?\NI'll make some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, uhh, that's okay.\NDon't do it on account of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Talk about unexpected...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.50,0:16:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've expected him to\Nbe as reckless as Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.54,0:16:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this sensible man can't\Npossibly be Luffy's brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a nice guy who\Ncares about his brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.18,0:16:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brothers can be so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is just full of surprises...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.22,0:16:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See! Aren't these guys neat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baroque Works!\NThose are the Billions' ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist Ace and Straw Hat Luffy!\NDon't think you can get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll show you just what Baroque\NWorks' Billions are made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.14,0:17:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy. I'll clean them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.55,0:17:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially in that little boat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see how skilled
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this Second Division Commander of\Nthe Whitebeard Pirates really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here he comes! Fire Fist Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try to get past five\Nof our ships, if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He jumped!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot him into the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.05,0:17:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.07,0:18:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.82,0:18:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy and his crew\Nare nowhere to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Tashigi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.23,0:18:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi was with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi? Princess Nefertari Vivi\Nwas with the Straw Hats?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.24,0:18:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They abducted the princess\Nfor some sort of scheme...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Vivi was acting like\Nshe was part of the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The princess? Part of their crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something really is\Nhappening in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:19:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. 11 was done in by someone\Nwhile he was tied up on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still haven't located\Nthe Straw Hats, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.17,0:19:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to fret. I have a good\Nidea of where they're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.70,0:19:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's after Crocodile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crocodile?! One of the\NSeven Warlords of the Sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.31,0:19:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the pirates given government approval?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know I hate the Seven Warlords.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.62,0:19:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially that detestable man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.42,0:19:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But standpoint-wise,\Nhe's a Navy and government ally!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.49,0:19:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always been a clever pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.99,0:19:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's never been the type to just\Nquietly obey the government!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tashigi! All you need\Nto remember is one thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate is a pirate,\Nno matter where he goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat will show\Nup wherever Crocodile is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.08,0:19:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things should become\Nclear if we go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And next time, you won't\Nget away, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Woohoo!\N--Ace is one of us now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.95,0:19:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.76,0:20:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who said I was joining you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.53,0:20:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's to delicious drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.83,0:20:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're always looking\Nfor an excuse to drink to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine is horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Are you sure you won't join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm chasing a certain man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.81,0:20:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name's Blackbeard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.48,0:20:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackbeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.78,0:20:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the pirate who\Nattacked the Drum Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.49,0:20:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He used to be a member of the 2nd\NDivision of the Whitebeard Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,one of my men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.62,0:20:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he committed the worst\Npossible sin on a pirate ship:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he killed a crewmember and jumped ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, as the commander,\NI gotta find and get rid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:49.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you're chasing after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here because I caught word\Nthat Blackbeard was seen in Yuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:21:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then your destination\Nis the same as ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've just entered the Sandora River.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we'll land at Erumalu, then\Nhead into the interior of Alabasta
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.29,0:21:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to reach Yuba here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The leader of the rebel army is in Yuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.09,0:21:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you're headed to Yuba next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll follow Nami-san and\NVivi-chan wherever they go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost, Love Cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what, you--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.14,0:21:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyways! It looks like we can\Ntravel together for a short while!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.21,0:21:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah! His brother\Nis more than welcome here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a fun time, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.19,0:21:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like the adventurers\NI dreamed of when I was a child
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I continue on to the ends of emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:22:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I scoop up my hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.08,0:22:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the sand and time\Nthat spills from them
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.72,0:22:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,show me that this is\Nwhat I was born to do
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's continue swimming\Nat a near-tumbling speed
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until we wash up someday\Non a white sandy beach
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one knows about
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:22:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Erumalu?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.53,0:23:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh? There's nothing here.\N--Erumalu, the City of Green...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The City of Green?!\NThere's no green anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.87,0:23:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a thriving city\Nuntil just recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.94,0:23:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karoo. I have an important\Nfavor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.91,0:23:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to go to Alubarna!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Erumalu, the City of Green,\Nand the Kung Fu Dugongs!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.98,0:23:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
